OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1776255072
OL,3,CScientists confirm fireball seen in
OL,4,Cnight skies was meteor
OL,6,FA video of the meteor blazing through
OL,7,Fthe night sky was captured by
OL,8,FNorthumberland Astro
OL,10,FScientists have confirmed that a
OL,11,Ffireball spotted in the skies above
OL,12,Fthe North East was a meteor.
OL,14,FThe impressive sight was captured by a
OL,15,Fnumber of cameras across the region at
OL,16,Faround 12.23am in the early hours of
OL,17,FMonday morning (13 April).
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
