CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1776255072
OL,3,CScientists confirm fireball seen in
OL,4,Cnight skies was meteor
OL,6,FThe International Meteor Organization
OL,7,Freceived reports of sightings of the
OL,8,Ffireball from members of the public in
OL,9,Fmany parts of the North East and North
OL,10,FYorkshire including Sunderland,
OL,11,FHartlepool, Stockton, Darlington and
OL,12,FScarborough.
OL,14,FJohn Maclean from the UK Meteor
OL,15,FObservation Network told ITV Tyne Tees
OL,16,Fthat their analysis has confirmed it
OL,17,Fwas a "sporadic meteor" which was not
OL,18,Flinked to any meteor shower.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
