OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1776255072
OL,3,CScientists confirm fireball seen in
OL,4,Cnight skies was meteor
OL,6,F"Meteorites derive from a variety of
OL,7,Fcelestial bodies, including asteroids
OL,8,Fand, more rarely, moons and planets.
OL,10,F"As such, meteorites can tell us a
OL,11,Fgreat deal about Solar System
OL,12,Fformation and how life emerged, which
OL,13,Fis why it is important for us to
OL,14,Frecover and study them."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
